            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>venison steaks</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong> and season generously with<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>venison steaks</strong> and cook for 2-3 minutes on each side for <strong>medium</strong> and 3-4 minutes on each side for<strong> medium-well done</strong></p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>venison</strong> to a plate and cover until serving, reserving the pan (and oil) for later</p>",
